
### 기본 주소
@host = http://localhost:8080

### Spring Security 기본 계정
@username = user
@password = 3fdbe547-b571-4b12-a5cd-715447777e84

### 테스트용 강좌 ID
@courseId = 1


### 1. 강좌 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/courses
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}


### 2. 강좌 등록
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "instructorId": 1,
  "title": "Java 기초 강좌",
  "description": "Java 기초 문법을 학습하는 강좌입니다.",
  "thumbnailUrl": "java.png",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}


### 3. 강좌 상세 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}


### 4. 강좌 수정
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/courses/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "title": "수정된 Java 강좌",
  "description": "수정된 강좌 설명입니다.",
  "thumbnailUrl": "updated-java.png",
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}


### 5. 강좌 삭제
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}


### 6. 삭제된 강좌 상세 조회 확인
GET {{host}}/api/v1/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}